\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">六、竞赛日程</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 15.75pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">、网络赛（预赛）：<span lang=\"EN-US\">2015</span>年<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">22</span>日<span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span>：<span lang=\"EN-US\">00-24</span>：<span lang=\"EN-US\">00</span>，地点不限</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 15.75pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">、现场赛（决赛）：<span lang=\"EN-US\">2015</span>年<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">29</span>日<span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span>：<span lang=\"EN-US\">00-14</span>：<span lang=\"EN-US\">00</span>，健行楼<span lang=\"EN-US\">A</span>楼二楼机房。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-right: 19.2pt; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 15.75pt;\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">七、竞赛题目及规则</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 15.75pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">．比赛试题：<span lang=\"EN-US\">8-12</span>题（中、英文）。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 15.75pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">．比赛时间：预赛为网络赛，共<span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span>小时，决赛为现场赛，共<span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span>小时。决赛比赛开始后，中途无故不得离开比赛区，否则做弃权处理。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 15.75pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">．试题的解答：要求参赛选手独自完成调试，完成后必须提交源代码，否则不算积分。解题顺序不作限制，提前完成、弃权允许提前离开比赛区。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 15.75pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">．竞赛编程环境为<span lang=\"EN-US\">VC6.0</span>。每个参赛选手使用一台计算机。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 15.75pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">5</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">．比赛允许携带非电子类资料，包括打印出来的程序、纸、笔记、教科书以及各类参考书、字典，禁止携带通讯工具。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 15.75pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">6</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">．在竞赛中，参赛选手不得通过网络工具（如</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;color:#333333;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">E-mail</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;color:#333333;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">BBS</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">等）以及任何其他方式和其他队伍的参赛选手交谈。一经发现，将取消其比赛资格。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 15.75pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">7.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">参赛选手不得出现妨碍比赛正常进行的行为，诸如擅自移动赛场中的设备，未经授权修改比赛软硬件，干扰他人比赛等。一经发现，将取消其比赛资格。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-right: 19.2pt; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 15.75pt;\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">八、评奖规则</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 15.75pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:#333333;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">对参赛队伍提交上来的程序，专家委员会本着公平、公正的原则，以如下规则评奖：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 15.75pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">1.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">比赛结果采用网上提交程序、电脑自动判断。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 15.75pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">2.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">按<span lang=\"EN-US\">ACM</span>程序设计竞赛规则，题目解答正确多者在前；若题数一样，则总时间（时间用时<span lang=\"EN-US\">+</span>罚时）数少的在前。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 15.75pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">3.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">比赛中可以查看实时排名，比赛结束后，将按照排名评奖。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-right: 19.2pt; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 15.75pt;\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">九、奖项设置</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-right: 19.2pt; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 15.75pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">拟设（以决赛名额计算）一等奖约<span lang=\"EN-US\">8%</span>、二等奖约<span lang=\"EN-US\">12%</span>、三等奖约<span lang=\"EN-US\">25%</span>，最终名额将由竞赛专家委员会根据实际情况进行确定。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-right: 19.2pt; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 15.75pt;\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">十、竞赛网站</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-right: 19.2pt; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 15.75pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">竞赛指定网站为<span lang=\"EN-US\">http://acm.zjut.edu.cn</span>，请随时关注网站信息。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-right: 19.2pt; text-indent: 24pt; line-