nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2015AK42&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 冯佳俊&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 三等奖</div>\r\n</div>', '1', '2016-03-18 18:56:42', '1388', '2015-03-30 09:57:58'), ('76', '1', '2015春季ACM集训报名（截止4月4日）', '<div><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">各位同学，ACM-ICPC程序设计竞赛2015春季集训报名开始啦！</span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">请抓紧时间报名，具体请点击链接：</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt;\"><a href=\"http://acm.zjut.edu.cn/system/hustojUserAction.do?method=saveUI&amp;mId=82DBE49892368943C2264B869BE0FEC7\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">2015春季集训报名</span></a></span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">报名截止4月4日。</span></div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '1', '2016-02-29 15:31:50', '449', '2015-03-30 13:26:33'), ('77', '1', '2015春季集训名单及计划', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">2015春季集训名单参见附件。</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">时间：下周日(4月12日)开始，每周日上午9:00开始。</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">地点：健行楼8号机房。</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>', '1', '2016-03-15 15:24:16', '412', '2015-04-06 13:37:10'), ('78', '1', '2015年浙江省程序设计竞赛参赛队员安排', '<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">经过竞赛团队选拔，李晟、徐世杰和单栋等21名同学将代表浙江工业大学参加2015年浙江省程序设计竞赛。</span><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">具体名单参见附件。</span></p>', '1', '2016-03-17 23:01:12', '909', '2015-04-06 13:41:25'), ('79', '1', '2015 C++通关考试（重考）报名公示', '<div>&nbsp;各位同学，2015&nbsp;C++通关考试（重考）报名列表公示参见附件，请仔细核对自己的信息，如有疑问请联系：acm@zjut.edu.cn。&nbsp;</div>', '1', '2016-03-18 14:03:03', '728', '2015-05-11 10:04:14'), ('80', '1', '2015 暑期集训计划和大一集训报名', '<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">大家好，暑期集训又要开始了，时间如下：</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">大一从7月21日至8月21日。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><br type=\"_moz\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">大二大三从7月6日至8月21日。</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">具体安排参见附件。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">特别注意：参加大一集训仍可报名，具体点击链接：<a href=\"http://acm.zjut.edu.cn/system/hustojUserAction.do?method=saveUI&amp;mId=048D220684D28C2895C922B5106CD34E\">暑期集训报名（大一）</a>。</span></p>', '1', '2016-03-16 19:54:36', '1153', '2015-06-23 22:29:01'), ('81', '1', '2015圣诞赛参赛名单公示', '<p>&nbsp;<span style=\"background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 25px; text-indent: 32px;\">&nbsp; 感谢大家的积极参与，</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: small; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 25px; text-indent: 32px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">2015圣诞赛报名已经全部结束，具体见附件。</span></p>\r\n<div style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 25px; text-indent: 32px; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245);\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-size: small;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;2015圣诞赛账号密码已经全部发送到报名同学相应的信箱，如有问题，请咨询acm_zjut@163.com。</span></div>', '1', '2016-03-18 15:32:51', '332', '2015-12-11 08:09:51'), ('82', '1', '2015迎新赛决赛名单公示', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size: larger;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">迎新赛决赛名单为预赛成绩解出</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">题或</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">题以上的学生（外加校集训队成员），具体名单参见附件。</span> <span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">发现有预赛作弊的，欢迎举报(acm_zjut@163.com)，如被证实将被取消决赛资格。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: larger;\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: larger;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '1', '2016-03-18 18:25:12', '306', '2015-12-14 18:01:01'), ('83', '1', '2015迎新赛决赛竞赛议程和竞赛规则', '<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">2015迎新赛决赛竞赛议程和竞赛规则参见附件。</span></p>', '1', '2016-03-18 15:32:40', '484', '2015-12-17 14:47:54'), ('84', '1', '2016校赛初赛参赛名单公示', '<p>&nbsp;2016校赛初赛参赛名单参见附件，有任何疑问请联系acm_zjut@163.com。</p>', '1', '2016-03-19 00:13:05', '8', '2016-03-18 19:52:02');
